THE CONCEPT
WAS AN IMMEDIATE HIT,

00:10:44,043 --> 00:10:46,179
AND NOW I HAVE A STAFF
OF OVER 70 GIRLS,

00:10:46,179 --> 00:10:48,948
AND WE WORK EVENTS AND
TOURNAMENTS FROM COAST TO COAST.

