AND ATTRACTIVE CADDIES.

00:11:50,043 --> 00:11:53,146
WE TRY TO EMPHASIZE
THE FUN FACTOR OF GOLF,

00:11:53,146 --> 00:11:54,214
BUT WE ALSO MAINTAIN

00:11:54,214 --> 00:11:56,149
A VERY PROFESSIONAL ATTITUDE
ABOUT GOLF.

00:11:56,149 --> 00:11:58,284
SHARKS, MY COMPANY
IS A HOLE IN ONE.

00:11:58,284 --> 00:12:02,021
SO WHICH ONE OF YOU
IS GONNA HELP ME...

00:12:02,021 --> 00:12:04,090
DRIVE MY COMPANY
TO THE GREEN?

00:12:04,090 --> 00:12:06,426
I'M CURIOUS.
WHERE DO YOU DO THIS?

00:12:06,426 --> 00:12:09,062
WE'RE BASED OUT OF
MYRTLE BEACH, SOUTH CAROLINA,

00:12:09,062 --> 00:12:10,263
BUT WE'VE ACTUALLY
BEEN EXPANDING

00:12:10,263 --> 00:12:12,465
TO OTHER MAJOR GOLF MARKETS,
SUCH AS SCOTTSDALE.

00:12:12,465 --> 00:12:16,436
WE EVEN HAVE CADDY GIRLS NOW
IN LOS ANGELES, MIAMI, ORLANDO,

00:12:16,436 --> 00:12:17,971
AND PARTS OF GEORGIA.

00:12:17,971 --> 00:12:19,072
MEGHAN, HOW BIG
IS YOUR BUSINESS?

00:12:19,072 --> 00:12:20,073
WHAT ARE YOUR REVENUES?

00:12:20,073 --> 00:12:24,143
IN 2013,
I HAD $148,000 IN SALES.

00:12:24,143 --> 00:12:25,078
GOOD FOR YOU.

00:12:25,078 --> 00:12:26,112
GOOD.
O'Leary: THAT'S NOT BAD.

00:12:26,112 --> 00:12:28,314
WE DID $34,000
IN SALES LAST MONTH.

00:12:28,314 --> 00:12:30,383
WHAT'S THE MAIN BULK
OF YOUR BUSINESS?

00:12:30,383 --> 00:12:33,119
IT COULD BE AN EVERYDAY
GOLF OUTING WITH FOUR GUYS.

00:12:33,119 --> 00:12:35,054
IT COULD BE A HUGE GOLF OUTING

00:12:35,054 --> 00:12:37,123
WITH 144 PLAYERS
IN A TOURNAMENT.

00:12:37,123 --> 00:12:39,192
WE'VE HAD
HUGE CORPORATE CLIENTS

00:12:39,192 --> 00:12:40,460
ACTUALLY HIRE UP TO 42 CADDIES
IN ONE DAY.

00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:42,061
O'Leary:
GIVE US THE NUMBERS.

00:12:42,061 --> 00:12:44,230
I CALL YOU UP.
I'VE GOT A CORPORATE EVENT.

00:12:44,230 --> 00:12:46,299
AND I WANT TO HIRE CADDIES
FOR EVERYBODY.

00:12:46,299 --> 00:12:50,103
THE LOWEST RATE THAT WE HAVE FOR
EACH CADDY IS $149 PER CADDY.

00:12:50,103 --> 00:12:52,105
WELL, YOU GET $149.
NOW, WHAT DO YOU PAY THEM?

00:12:52,105 --> 00:12:54,040
I PAY EVERY CADDY $100.

00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:55,308
Greiner: IS THAT FOR 9 HOLES?
18 HOLES?

00:12:55,308 --> 00:12:56,976
18 HOLES.
18 HOLES.

00:12:56,976 --> 00:12:58,111
9 HOLES IS $89.

00:12:58,111 --> 00:13:00,079
MEGHAN, HOW'D YOU COME UP
WITH THE IDEA?

00:13:00,079 --> 00:13:02,115
I WAS, HONESTLY, IN COLLEGE
AND COMPLETELY BROKE.

00:13:02,115 --> 00:13:03,383
I WAS BARTENDING
IN MYRTLE BEACH,

00:13:03,383 --> 00:13:05,285
WHERE THERE'S
A HUNDRED GOLF COURSES,

00:13:05,285 --> 00:13:07,220
AND I NOTICED
THAT I REALLY LIKED GOLFERS.

00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:09,489
THEY TIPPED THE BEST, AND ONE
GROUP CAME UP TO ME ONE NIGHT,

00:13:09,489 --> 00:13:12,425
AND THEY'RE LIKE, "HEY,
WE WANT YOU TO COME
GOLF WITH US TOMORROW.

00:13:12,425 --> 00:13:14,260
WE'LL PAY YOU."
AND I'M LIKE, "THAT'S WEIRD."

00:13:14,260 --> 00:13:15,428
[ LAUGHTER ]
BUT HERE'S THE THING --

00:13:15,428 --> 00:13:17,230
A LIGHT BULB WENT OF,
AND I WAS LIKE,

00:13:17,230 --> 00:13:20,099
"YOU KNOW, IT WOULD BE
REALLY AWESOME IF I
MAKE MY OWN SCHEDULE.

00:13:20,099 --> 00:13:21,301
"I WANT TO BE
OUT ON THE GOLF COURSE

00:13:21,301 --> 00:13:23,036
AND TAKE ADVANTAGE
OF THIS MARKET."

00:13:23,036 --> 00:13:27,206
MEGHAN, TAKE THIS QUESTION
THE ABSOLUTE MOST INNOCENT WAY.

00:13:27,206 --> 00:13:28,441
MOST GUYS ARE PIGS.

00:13:28,441 --> 00:13:31,077
SPEAK FOR YOURSELF,
COCHON.

00:13:31,077 --> 00:13:32,378
WHEN THEY'RE HIRING
THE BEAUTIFUL LADIES --

00:13:32,378 --> 00:13:34,147
I DON'T MEAN THIS
IN A DISRESPECTFUL WAY --

00:13:34,147 --> 00:13:37,183
ARE THEY HIRING THEM FOR GOLF,
OR IS IT JUST A FUN THING?

00:13:37,183 --> 00:13:38,318
WE ARE NOT PEOPLE TO COME

00:13:38,318 --> 00:13:40,053
AND GET HIRED TO HANG OUT
WITH GUYS, OKAY?

00:13:40,053 --> 00:13:41,154
LIKE, OUR WHOLE NICHE

00:13:41,154 --> 00:13:43,122
IS THAT WE ARE HOT GIRLS
THAT KNOW ABOUT GOLF.

00:13:43,122 --> 00:13:45,291
DO YOU DO TRADITIONAL
CADDY THINGS?

00:13:45,291 --> 00:13:47,427
YES. WE'RE GETTING YOUR CLUBS
TO AND FROM YOU.

00:13:47,427 --> 00:13:49,495
WE'RE FIXING PITCH MARKS.
WE'RE RAKING EVERY SAND TRAP.

00:13:49,495 --> 00:13:50,463
WE'RE TENDING THE PIN.

00:13:50,463 --> 00:13:52,298
WE'RE HELPING YOU
GET YOUR YARDAGE.

00:13:52,298 --> 00:13:55,001
EVERYTHING THAT A CADDY
WOULD NORMALLY DO, WE DO THAT.

00:13:55,001 --> 00:13:56,402
WE JUST HAD FOUR OF OUR GIRLS
CONTRACTED

00:13:56,402 --> 00:13:58,404
FOR THE PGA-SANCTIONED
NATIONAL CHAMPIONSHIP

00:13:58,404 --> 00:13:59,439
COMING UP IN TWO WEEKS.

00:13:59,439 --> 00:14:01,040
THAT'S GONNA BE TELEVISED.

00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,342
FOUR OF MY GIRLS
ARE CARRYING BAGS.

00:14:02,342 --> 00:14:06,179
HOW DO YOU MAKE THIS MORE THAN
A REGIONALLY BASED BUSINESS?

00:14:06,179 --> 00:14:09,415
A STANDARD GOLF TOURNAMENT
HAS 144 PLAYERS.

00:14:09,415 --> 00:14:10,983
THAT'S 144 PEOPLE THAT GO HOME

00:14:10,983 --> 00:14:12,218
AND TELL THEIR GOLF BUDDIES
ABOUT IT,

00:14:12,218 --> 00:14:13,386
AND THEN IT'S JUST --
IT SPREADS.

00:14:13,386 --> 00:14:17,090
HALF OF OUR BUSINESS THIS YEAR
WAS REPEAT BUSINESS.

00:14:17,090 --> 00:14:18,224
AND BIG CORPORATE TOURNAMENTS,

00:14:18,224 --> 00:14:20,493
WE ALREADY HAVE SOME LINED UP
THROUGH DECEMBER.

00:14:20,493 --> 00:14:23,062
AND THIS IS NOT JUST, LIKE,
ONE OR TWO GIRLS GOING OUT.

00:14:23,062 --> 00:14:25,098
THIS IS 30 TO 40 GIRLS
GOING OUT, YOU KNOW, IN ONE DAY.

00:14:25,098 --> 00:14:27,400
$100,000 FOR 20%.

00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:29,435
YOU THINK THIS IS WORTH
HALF A MILLION BUCKS?

00:14:29,435 --> 00:14:32,205
YOU HAVE TO LOOK AT
THE LIFETIME CUSTOMER VALUE.

00:14:32,205 --> 00:14:33,406
GOLF ISN'T GOING ANYWHERE.

00:14:33,406 --> 00:14:35,408
THE USE OF ATTRACTIVE PEOPLE
ISN'T GOING ANYWHERE.

00:14:35,408 --> 00:14:38,211
AND WE HAVE A DATABASE
OF THOUSANDS OF CUSTOMERS

00:14:38,211 --> 00:14:40,079
THAT HAVE USED US
IN THE PAST.

00:14:40,079 --> 00:14:41,147
EVERYTHING'S GREAT.

00:14:41,147 --> 00:14:42,415
I HAVE 70 GIRLS WORKING,
BOOKINGS EVERY DAY.

00:14:42,415 --> 00:14:45,051
I WANT TO TAKE THAT
AND EXPAND THAT TO OTHER PLACES.

00:14:45,051 --> 00:14:47,053
BUT WE ALSO HAVE PEOPLE
ASKING FOR CADDIES

00:14:47,053 --> 00:14:48,154
IN CHICAGO, MINNEAPOLIS --

00:14:48,154 --> 00:14:50,223
ALL THESE AREAS
THAT I WOULD LOVE TO GET INTO.

00:14:50,223 --> 00:14:53,459
Greiner:
YOU KNOW, FOR ME, I JUST SEE
SO MANY ISSUES OR PROBLEMS

00:14:53,459 --> 00:14:56,062
THAT I COULD FORESEE HAPPENING
WITH THIS.

00:14:56,062 --> 00:14:59,098
IT WORRIES ME SOMETIMES,
JUST FOR YOU GUYS, PERIOD,

00:14:59,098 --> 00:15:01,067
TO BE OUT THERE WITH
THE DRINKING AND THIS AND THAT.

00:15:01,067 --> 00:15:04,070
I -- IT'S JUST NOT A BUSINESS
I COULD GET BEHIND.

00:15:04,070 --> 00:15:07,039
SO FOR THAT REASON,
I'M OUT.

00:15:07,039 --> 00:15:09,008
I UNDERSTAND.

00:15:09,008 --> 00:15:12,245
AND THAT'S WHY WE HAVE VERY,
VERY STRICT STANDARDS OF CONDUCT

00:15:12,245 --> 00:15:13,279
FOR ALL OF OUR CADDIES.

00:15:13,279 --> 00:15:14,981
AND I THINK WITH ANY JOB PLACE,

00:15:14,981 --> 00:15:17,049
YOU HAVE A LIABILITY
FOR ANY KIND OF HARASSMENT

00:15:17,049 --> 00:15:18,084
OR ANYTHING THAT CAN GO ON.

00:15:18,084 --> 00:15:19,352
IT CAN HAPPEN ANYWHERE.

00:15:19,352 --> 00:15:21,220
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
MEGHAN, LET ME --
LET ME JUMP IN HERE.

00:15:21,220 --> 00:15:25,091
I THINK YOU CAN TURN THIS
INTO SOMETHING SPECIAL.

00:15:25,091 --> 00:15:27,193
BUT I HATE GOLF,
SO I'M OUT.

00:15:27,193 --> 00:15:28,428
[ LAUGHS ]

00:15:28,428 --> 00:15:30,062
WE COULD MAKE YOU LIKE GOLF
A LITTLE BIT MORE.

00:15:30,062 --> 00:15:31,330
MAYBE IF YOU HAD A CADDY GIRL
WITH YOU, YOU'D LIKE IT.

00:15:31,330 --> 00:15:33,299
THIS IS SUPER FUN.
