A HUNDRED THOUSAND THINGS

00:15:33,299 --> 00:15:38,137
I WOULD RATHER DO THAN
SCHLEP AROUND A GOLF COURSE.

00:15:38,137 --> 00:15:40,440
John: YOU KNOW, JUST LIKE MARK,
I-I DON'T LIKE GOLF.

00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:42,442
BUT I-I LIKE THE CONCEPT.

00:15:42,442 --> 00:15:45,178
I THINK YOU'RE IN
A TOUGH POSITION,

00:15:45,178 --> 00:15:48,414
BECAUSE, FIRST OF ALL,
YOU DO NEED TO EXPAND

00:15:48,414 --> 00:15:50,349
BECAUSE SOMEBODY ELSE WILL TRY
TO COME UP WITH THE IDEA

00:15:50,349 --> 00:15:52,051
AND BE YOUR COMPETITION.

00:15:52,051 --> 00:15:55,288
BUT ON THE OTHER HAND,
YOU SPREAD YOURSELF TOO THIN...

00:15:55,288 --> 00:15:57,423
YOU'RE NOT GONNA MAKE
ENOUGH MONEY IN EACH MARKET.

00:15:57,423 --> 00:16:00,460
I THINK THERE'S
TOO MUCH WORK HERE.

00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:03,296
SO I'D HAVE TO BE OUT.

00:16:03,296 --> 00:16:06,232
THANK YOU.

00:16:06,232 --> 00:16:08,301
Herjavec: SO, I-I THINK
YOU'VE GOT A GREAT BUSINESS.

00:16:08,301 --> 00:16:09,969
YOU'VE BUILT IT
FROM NOTHING.

00:16:09,969 --> 00:16:13,072
BUT EVERY BUSINESS IS A LIVING,
BREATHING THING,

00:16:13,072 --> 00:16:15,374
AND IT GOES THROUGH
DIFFERENT STAGES.

00:16:15,374 --> 00:16:18,044
THERE'S THE HUSTLE STAGE,

00:16:18,044 --> 00:16:21,214
WHERE YOU NEED MORE HUSTLE,
MORE TIME,

00:16:21,214 --> 00:16:24,283
AND YOU JUST GOT TO FIND MORE
HOURS THAN THE 24 YOU'RE GIVEN.

00:16:24,283 --> 00:16:29,155
AND THEN SOME BUSINESSES
GET TO THE INVESTMENT STAGE.

00:16:29,155 --> 00:16:31,257
YOU'RE IN THE HUSTLE STAGE.

00:16:31,257 --> 00:16:33,159
I DON'T --
YOU DIDN'T
DO A GOOD JOB TODAY

00:16:33,159 --> 00:16:36,329
OF TELLING ME HOW,
AS AN INVESTOR,

00:16:36,329 --> 00:16:39,265
I GIVE YOU $100,000 AND YOU
MAKE THE BUSINESS GO BOOM.

00:16:39,265 --> 00:16:41,167
YOU GOT LOTS OF HUSTLE.

00:16:41,167 --> 00:16:43,135
I WAS --
SO KEEP GOING.

00:16:43,135 --> 00:16:44,303
BUT I'M OUT.

00:16:46,439 --> 00:16:48,241
ALL RIGHT.
WHO'S LEFT?

00:16:48,241 --> 00:16:50,376
IT'S JUST YOU,
THE WORST GOLFER IN THE WORLD.
MR. WONDERFUL.

00:16:50,376 --> 00:16:53,279
HE'S OUR IDEAL CUSTOMER.
HE'S PERFECT. SHOWS UP GRUMPY.

00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:56,182
