[ LAUGHTER ]

00:16:56,182 --> 00:16:58,050
BUT, MEGHAN,
HE'S GRUMPY ALL THE TIME.

00:16:58,050 --> 00:16:59,352
I ACTUALLY --
I'M VERY IMPRESSED WITH YOU

00:16:59,352 --> 00:17:01,454
BECAUSE I THOUGHT
THIS PRESENTATION

00:17:01,454 --> 00:17:03,422
WAS GOING TO BE
JUST RIDICULOUS.

00:17:03,422 --> 00:17:05,057
AND YOU COME BACK...

00:17:05,057 --> 00:17:06,092
DID A GOOD JOB.
...AND DID A PRETTY GOOD JOB.

00:17:06,092 --> 00:17:07,026
YEAH.
YOU DID.

00:17:07,026 --> 00:17:07,493
SO GOOD FOR YOU.

00:17:07,493 --> 00:17:10,263
BUT, YOU KNOW,
IS IT INVESTABLE?

00:17:10,263 --> 00:17:13,266
I GIVE YOU $100,000, I DON'T
KNOW HOW I EVER GET IT BACK.

00:17:13,266 --> 00:17:14,367
THAT'S THE PROBLEM.

00:17:14,367 --> 00:17:17,370
AT OUR GROWTH RATE OF 30%
EVERY YEAR AS AN AVERAGE,

00:17:17,370 --> 00:17:20,106
YOU WOULD GET IT BACK
WITHIN FOUR YEARS EASILY.

00:17:20,106 --> 00:17:22,074
THE ONLY THING THAT MATTERS
IN BUSINESS IS CASH.

00:17:22,074 --> 00:17:24,243
WHEN IT LEAVES -- AND RIGHT NOW
IT'S AROUND MY ANKLE GOING,

00:17:24,243 --> 00:17:27,380
"DADDY, NO! DADDY, NO!" --
AND I GIVE IT TO YOU...

