THAT I OUTLINED,

00:36:33,792 --> 00:36:35,528
I DO FEEL
IT'S A FAIR VALUE.

00:36:35,528 --> 00:36:37,830
NOBODY'S GONNA PAY YOU
MORE THAN FIVE TIMES
YOUR CASH FLOW FOR THIS.

00:36:37,830 --> 00:36:38,864
THEY JUST WON'T.

00:36:38,864 --> 00:36:40,900
THE ONLY MISTAKE
YOU'VE MADE

00:36:40,900 --> 00:36:43,569
IS YOU'VE -- YOU'VE PUT
A 100% PREMIUM ON IT,

00:36:43,569 --> 00:36:47,606
AND YET YOU WANT A SHARK SO THAT
THEY CAN ADD THEIR VALUE.

00:36:47,606 --> 00:36:49,608
VERY DIFFICULT TO DO THAT.

00:36:49,608 --> 00:36:50,843
I MEAN, IT'S A --
IT'S A MISTAKE.

