00:36:59,818 --> 00:37:01,921
JUST MY PERSONAL THING.

00:37:01,921 --> 00:37:02,821
I'M OUT.

00:37:03,689 --> 00:37:05,491
THANK YOU
FOR YOUR TIME, LORI.
THANK YOU.

00:37:05,491 --> 00:37:07,626
