A MORE REASONABLE VALUE

00:37:43,662 --> 00:37:45,698
THAT YOU HAD
ON THIS BUSINESS.

00:37:45,698 --> 00:37:47,533
JUST LIKE ANY GREAT LOVE AFFAIR,

00:37:47,533 --> 00:37:49,735
YOU'VE GOT TO HAVE SOME SENSE
OF REALITY TO IT.

00:37:50,869 --> 00:37:52,438
I'M OUT.

00:37:52,438 --> 00:37:54,707
YOU HAVE TWO SHARKS LEFT.

00:37:54,707 --> 00:37:56,809
YOU SHOULD FOCUS YOUR ENERGIES
ON THEM.

00:37:58,577 --> 00:37:59,645
W-- YOU KNOW, WE --

